Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anata no koto ga daisuki{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nee, uso wa tsukenai{\i0}
