Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.76,0:23:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't go adding things to my name!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.01,0:23:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ha! "Big dummy" is\Ngood enough for you then!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.98,0:23:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You called me "big dummy" again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll say it as many times as I want!{\i0}
